    "description": "Join the 1mg Capital India family as a Backend Developer in Ranchi. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout 1mg Capital India:\n1mg Capital India is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in Git\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Referral bonus program\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ranchi, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with 1mg Capital India!",
